        <p>You can use macros in <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> to automate frequently used commands or processes. After you record a macro, you can play it back to perform all of the steps in the macro with a single action. You can also assign a shortcut to the macro<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare-Online-Only"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Editor-Tools/Shortcuts/Changing-Hot-Keys.htm">Changing Hot Keys</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Contributor-Online-Only"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Contributor/Editor-Tools/Shortcuts/Changing-Hot-Keys.htm">Changing Hot Keys</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>, add it to the Quick Access Toolbar<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare-Online-Only"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Interface/Ribbons-Toolbars-Menus/Quick-Access-Toolbar.htm">Quick Access Toolbar</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Contributor-Online-Only"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Contributor/Interface/Ribbons-Toolbars-Menus/Quick-Access-Toolbar.htm">Quick Access Toolbar</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>, or access it from the Quick Launch bar<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare-Online-Only"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Interface/Ribbons-Toolbars-Menus/Quick-Launch-Bar.htm">Quick Launch Bar</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Contributor-Online-Only"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Contributor/Interface/Ribbons-Toolbars-Menus/Quick-Launch-Bar.htm">Quick Launch Bar</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>.</p>
